      <title>印度希望与以前从未见过的“紧迫性”达成交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/india-wants-trade-deal-with-us-with-an-urgency-not-seen-before</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳伦德拉·莫迪（Narendra Modi）政府的一名部长说，印度的贸易团队“真的被收费”，并希望与美国迅速达成双边交易，因为南亚国家争先恐后地避免了华盛顿的不断变化，不断融合的关税策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/india-wants-trade-deal-with-us-with-an-urgency-not-seen-before</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 08:12:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
